7 PART III. SEVERABILITY CLAUSE AND EFFECTIVE DATE
8 SECTION 6. Severability. – If any provision of this act or its application is held
9 invalid, the invalidity does not affect other provisions or applications of this act that can be given
10 effect without the invalid provisions or application and, to this end, the provisions of this act are
11 severable.
12 SECTION 7. Effective Date. – Except as otherwise provided, this act is effective
13 when it becomes law.
